OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloudier in
OL,6,Fthe east with some outbreaks of rain
OL,7,Fand drier interludes. Otherwise bright
OL,8,Fthen clear spells and a few showers
OL,9,Fcoming in from the west.
OL,10,
OL,11,CMonday:FDry for many with bright
OL,12,Fspells, though a few showers are
OL,13,Fpossible, some of which may be heavy.
OL,14,FMore frequent showers will spread into
OL,15,Fthe west during the evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
