OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FBright
OL,6,For sunny spells and scattered showers
OL,7,Fon Tuesday and Wednesday, these heavy
OL,8,Fand thundery at times. Widespread
OL,9,Fcloud and rain arriving from the west
OL,10,Fon Thursday.
